Recorded and mixed at The Farm, Surrey.

Includes English inner sleeve and Japanese insert.

Manufactured and Distributed by Nippon Phonogram Co., Ltd. Tokyo
℗ 1981 Made in Japan

Some or maybe all copies are black/dark brown translucent, under a bright light source.

Embrossed cover front.
